Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Trooper Jill E. Mattice Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the village of Morris as the "Trooper Jill E. Mattice Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Trooper Jill E. Mattice Memorial Highway"
